* Run on Windows
   We use MFC to developing GUI.
   Preconditions: install mingw for compiling the program
   Steps:
     1. cd windowpopup/
     2. gcc -o main.exe main.c
* Run on Linux
   We use GTK to developing GUI.
   Preconditions: install gtk lib.
  Steps:
     1. cd windowpopup/
     2. gcc `pkg-config --cflags --libs gtk+-2.0` main.c -o main
